<h2>Blue Sky</h2>

<div>
	<h3>Ingredients</h3>

	<ul>
		<li>1 part Blue Curacao liqueur</li>
		<li>2 parts bitter lemon soda</li>
		<li>Ice cubes</li>
	</ul>
</div>

<div>
	<h3>Method</h3>

	<ul>
		<li>Mix in a highball glass. Stir. Garnish with a slice of lemon</li>
	</ul>
</div>

Link to this recipe: http://jsrn.net/tablecloth/#cocktails/bluesky
